  "body": "I need to set some annotations to literal string `true` rather than boolean of truth. Currently there is no way to do it since the value `true`, `false` and numbers get parsed into their typed values.\r\n\r\nThe issue can be reproduced for nginx-ingress chart for example:\r\n\r\n```\r\nhelm install stable/nginx-ingress --set controller.podAnnotations.prometheus\\\\.io/scrape=true\r\n```",
